reviewText: Kids tolerated it, but for me it was painful

Back in 5th grade i was in this awesome video called Uncle Nick and the Magic Forest, Happy Day Parade.  what a great video.  its cheesy, but the little ones will enjoy it.  And I know this from experience cause I showed it to the kids at the preschool I work at and they loved it.  Lots of singing and dancing for the kids to do with the video.
